title: Journal of the American Dental Association
aka: Journal of the American Dental Association and The Dental Cosmos

preceded-by.note: The Journal of the National Dental Association

additional-note: After absorbing The Dental Cosmos, this journal was published as Journal of the American Dental Association and The Dental Cosmos in 1937 and 1938, before returning to its earlier name.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Felice Gollotti for copyright research on this title.
